A '''quillarat''' was a creature native to [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]]. [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] caught one with his bare hands and gave it to [[Mallatobuck/Legends|Mallatobuck]] prior to their marriage as a sign of his love.<ref name="The New Jedi Order: Agents of Chaos I: Hero's Trial">''[[The New Jedi Order: Agents of Chaos I: Hero's Trial]]''</ref>

